Full message: Install expo-contacts; add READ_CONTACTS (Android) and NSContactsUsageDescription (iOS) permissions. Trusted contact modal now has Choose from contacts button that opens native contact picker. Fix support tab not reflecting trusted contact after it is set in account: switch useEffect to useFocusEffect so the data re-fetches on every tab focus. Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
